dct_title_s: Plan and Profile for Tunnel from Main Quadrangle to Dormitory.  F.L. Olmsted & Co., Landscape Archtects
dct_description_sm: Oversize; Tunnel from inner quad to (Encina?) dormitory location.  Outline for east lateral quad, suggestion of 8 houses in front of said quad.  Detail of tunnel.  Tunnel to be under Land J.
